> data to cite around how this data-driven approach is critical for making
> true change within organizations at scale.
>
> This is a critical insight as companies work to incorporate D&I campaigns
> with distributed workforces while acquiring increasing amounts of data on
> same. I.e., it's easy to get the data, and even easier to use it in ways
> that damage rather than reinforce your D&I efforts.
>
> This case study will demonstrate how companies can approach the use of
> detailed analytics to improve D&I outcomes and drive positive corporate
> culture change, providing specific examples they can use directly.
>
> This work builds on the collaboration between Indigometrics and Bechtel
> over the last year+ focused on this topic. Indigometrics has been solely
