> my last two books - Reputation Economics (McMillan) and Hacking Work
> (Penguin) - as well as my consulting work to Fortune-500 executives from =
BP
> to Ford to Merck.
>
> We wanted to offer this to HBR before approaching any other outlets. Adi,
> you've always been kind to me - even when I've pitched crazy off-the-wall
> ideas to you out of nowhere - and I trust your judgement. Let me know if
> this is worth pursuing!
>
> Many thanks,
> Josh Klein
